quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  40,21,Kodi iwo sadayende pa dziko lapansi ndi kuona zimene zidawachitikira anthu a makedzana? Iwo adali a mphamvu kuposa awa. Koma Mulungu adawalanga chifukwa cha zoipa zawo. Ndipo iwo adalibe wina aliyense wowateteza kwa Mulungu
  40,22,Ichi ndi chifukwa chakuti Atumwi awo adadza kwa iwo ndi zizindikiro zooneka ndi maso koma iwo adakana Atumwiwo. Kotero Mulungu adawaononga iwo. Ndithudi! Iye ndi Wamphamvu ndipo chilango chake ndi chowawa kwambiri
  40,23,"Ndipo, ndithudi, tidamutumiza Mose ndi uthenga wathu ndi ulamuliro wooneka"
  40,24,"Kwa Farawo, Hamani ndi Karuni koma iwo adati, “Munthu wamatsenga ndi wabodza.”"
  40,25,"Ndipo pamene iye adawauza choonadi chochokera kwa Ife, iwo adati, “Iphani ana onse aamuna a anthu amene akhulupirira ndi iye ndipo musunge ana awo aakazi.” Koma ziwembu za anthu osakhulupirira sizitha bwino chifukwa zilibe maziko enieni"
  40,26,"Ndipo Farawo adati, “Mundisiye ine kuti ndiphe Mose ndipo musiyeni iye kuti apemphe kwa Ambuye wake. Ndithudi ine ndiopa kuti iye adzasintha chipembedzo chanu ndi kuyambitsa chisokonezo m’dziko.”"
  40,27,"Ndipo Mose adati, “Ndithudi ine ndithawira kwa Ambuye wanga ndi Ambuye wanu kuti anditeteze kwa aliyense wamwano amene sakhulupirira mu tsiku lachiweruzo.”"